lu.uni.geko.weaver
Class HashMappedAdvice

java.lang.Object
  lu.uni.geko.weaver.HashMappedAdvice
All Implemented Interfaces:
Advice
public class HashMappedAdvice
extends Object
implements Advice

An implementation of the convenience representation (or proxy) of an Advice that uses a HashMap to map advice content elements to their advice instantiation scope.

Attention: The collections returned by this implementation are backed up. Changing the returned collections will change collections of this implementation.

See Also:
AdviceInstantiationScope
